org.jamsim.ascape.navigator
Class MicroSimScapeNode

java.lang.Object
  javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
      org.ascape.runtime.swing.navigator.ScapeNode
          org.jamsim.ascape.navigator.MicroSimScapeNode
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, MutableTreeNode, TreeNode
public class MicroSimScapeNode
extends org.ascape.runtime.swing.navigator.ScapeNode

Navigator tree node for a MicroSimScape. Same as ScapeNode but in addition:

  • creates a "Datasets" node child with PanelViewNodes for all the data in the scape
  • creates an "Output Tables" node and exposes access to this node so scapes can add tables during or after the simulation run

$Revision$
Author:
Oliver Mannion
